@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rrepqf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.cos(tmp + 0.83) * 0.79))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v2 + 0.98) * v0))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.16) * (tmp + 0.79 + v0 + 0.88)) / v0)
    v2 = ((v1 + (v2 + 0.67 * v1 + 0.87)) - wp.exp((v0 + 0.85 - v2 + 0.29)))
    v2 = ((v0 - wp.sin(v0 + 0.04)) - ((v1 + 0.59 - v2 + 0.30) + 0.58))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.57)) + wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.20)))
    data[tid] = v0
